 show this decline in the workforce of 
 our local pits:                       
{                                      
{Collieries            1960     1985   
{__________            ____     _____  
{                                      
 Upton                 2500    Closed  
 Frickley              3500     1300   
 South Kirkby          2800     1100   
 Kinsley Drift         1700      600   
 Ferrymoor Riddings     __       400   
                      _____    _____   
                     {10500     3400}  
                                       
  This sample of figures shows that in 
 1960 more men were employed in        
{Frickley Colliery }alone than the     
 collective workforce of{all}the       
 collieries in our area in 1985.       
                                       
